# game/Scenes/CafeChats/cafechat0.rpy:6
translate portuguese cafechat0_6189c630:

    # "I hang around the café for a while, looking for somebody who might be up for a chat."
    "Fico por um tempo no café, à procura de alguém que possa estar a fim de conversar."

# game/Scenes/CafeChats/cafechat0.rpy:8
translate portuguese cafechat0_a701de0e:

    # "Eventually, a cute woman comes in and sits by herself, working on her laptop."
    "Por fim, uma mulher gira entra e senta-se sozinha, a trabalhar no seu portátil."

# game/Scenes/CafeChats/cafechat0.rpy:9
translate portuguese cafechat0_87d5764a:

    # "I decide that she's the one and walk up to her."
    "Decido que é ela e aproximo-me."

# game/Scenes/CafeChats/cafechat0.rpy:10
translate portuguese cafechat0_b5117939:

    # "She glances up at me as I approach, and gives me an annoyed look."
    "Ela olha para mim quando me aproximo e lança-me um olhar irritado."

# game/Scenes/CafeChats/cafechat0.rpy:11
translate portuguese cafechat0_d7cfad11:

    # "I don't let that stop me though. I continue up towards her."
    "Mas não deixo que isso me impeça. Continuo a aproximar-me."

# game/Scenes/CafeChats/cafechat0.rpy:12
translate portuguese cafechat0_f2795711:

    # pc "Uh, hello."
    pc "Uh, olá."

# game/Scenes/CafeChats/cafechat0.rpy:13
translate portuguese cafechat0_ef39114d:

    # pc "I just noticed you from across the café. I love your hair."
    pc "Acabei de te ver do outro lado do café. Adoro o teu cabelo."

# game/Scenes/CafeChats/cafechat0.rpy:14
translate portuguese cafechat0_944c8247:

    # "Woman" "Yeah, hold on a second, babe, there's some jerk here trying to talk to me."
    "Woman" "Sim, espera um segundo, querido, há aqui um idiota a tentar falar comigo."

# game/Scenes/CafeChats/cafechat0.rpy:16
translate portuguese cafechat0_ef7a4ba1:

    # "She looks up at me and points to the bluetooth headset that's in her ear."
    "Ela olha para mim e aponta para o auricular Bluetooth que tem no ouvido."

# game/Scenes/CafeChats/cafechat0.rpy:17
translate portuguese cafechat0_3193f415:

    # "Woman" "Hey, I'm kinda busy here, guy."
    "Woman" "Ei, estou um pouco ocupada, meu."

# game/Scenes/CafeChats/cafechat0.rpy:18
translate portuguese cafechat0_b2b83740:

    # "Woman" "Do I look like I would be interested in talking to some rando that walks up to me in a café?"
    "Woman" "Pareço-te alguém que estaria interessada em falar com um desconhecido que se aproxima de mim num café?"

# game/Scenes/CafeChats/cafechat0.rpy:19
translate portuguese cafechat0_3d85290d:

    # "Woman" "Go on. Leave me alone."
    "Woman" "Vai-te embora. Deixa-me em paz."

# game/Scenes/CafeChats/cafechat0.rpy:20
translate portuguese cafechat0_4f0c7c77:

    # pc "Right, sorry."
    pc "Certo, desculpa."

# game/Scenes/CafeChats/cafechat0.rpy:22
translate portuguese cafechat0_42bd03ba:

    # "I walk away and don't bother her anymore."
    "Afasto-me e não a incomodo mais."

# game/Scenes/CafeChats/cafechat0.rpy:23
translate portuguese cafechat0_888bf925:

    # "You would think that I would feel defeated after a rejection like that, but I don't."
    "Seria de esperar que me sentisse derrotado depois de uma rejeição dessas, mas não me sinto."

# game/Scenes/CafeChats/cafechat0.rpy:24
translate portuguese cafechat0_26026dae:

    # "I feel more confident actually. I had been rejected - harshly rejected - but I'm still alive. I can deal with it."
    "Na verdade, sinto-me mais confiante. Fui rejeitado — rejeitado de forma dura — mas continuo vivo. Consigo lidar com isso."

# game/Scenes/CafeChats/cafechat0.rpy:25
translate portuguese cafechat0_ed9a1144:

    # "I should try that again sometime, though hopefully with a nicer person."
    "Devia tentar isso outra vez algum dia, embora, espero, com uma pessoa mais simpática."

# game/Scenes/CafeChats/cafechat0.rpy:31
translate portuguese cafechat0_73e222e6:

    # "For now, I head to class."
    "Por agora, vou para a aula."

# game/Scenes/CafeChats/cafechat0.rpy:34
translate portuguese cafechat0_fbe64787:

    # "For now, I head back to my car."
    "Por agora, volto para o meu carro."

